    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出起点：Auto-instrumenter通过OTLP连接到OpenTelemetry receiver。接下来Alloy内部怎么处理？",
